
DSO (Dynamically Shared Object)
-------------------------------

Support for dynamically loadable modules, known as DSO modules or "shared"
modules, is now available in ProFTPD 1.3.0.

  --enable-dso
  --with-shared
  --libexecdir/ModulePath
  LoadModule, ModuleOrder

  Importance of keeping access to ModulePath/libexec dir restricted
